  "description": "This individual is a human male corpse-revenant preserved by the cavern’s chill, with pale skinTone stretched tight over sharp cheekbones and a slightly slackened jaw. Gray eyes sit deep in bruised sockets and fix forward with an unblinking, funerary stillness. Black hair hangs in long, damp ropes, broken by a bare strip of scalp where the flesh has torn away. The frame is lean and desiccated, marked by old fractures that have healed crookedly and grant the gait a permanent, dragging asymmetry.",
